{"tid":991474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[秒經] 對住地鐵廢老真係要零容忍","createTime":"2019-01-22T11:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T15:53:31.000Z","uid":183601,"like":65,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d8a34af131a18498dd98fd676a4d66ac082c8e6c","tid":991474,"uid":183601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T11:42:33.000Z","msg":"話說今日搭地鐵<br />\n去到大圍好多人準備上車<br />\n當時車廂入面已經逼逼地, d人都準備企入d<br />\n我就企喺最入靠門塊玻璃度挨住<br />\n有個後生仔企我隔離<br />\n好喇, 咁大圍d人開始上車行入黎<br />\n有個呀嬋左穿右插咁搵位<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">企</span></span><br />\n佢見到我隔離個後生仔再隔離有個吉位可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">企到一個人</span></span><br />\n個呀嬋就嚟料喇<br />\n呀嬋&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後生仔&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 你唔入我入, 唔好得住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 唔識出聲呀!?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我而家咪出聲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 你出聲係話我得撚住你呀! 你有叫我借借咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我唔講粗口架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 屌7柒你緊係要講粗口啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我唔同你呢d無教養嘅人講野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 收嗲啦仲喺度ee吟吟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個呀嬋就真係收咗嗲 <br />\n嗱, 個男仔雖然唔高, 但勝在夠霸氣, 幾句就屌到個廢老呀嬋收皮<br />\n屌你老尾而家d死廢老用2蚊搭車都嫌你企埋一邊都係阻撚住佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我喺度特此表揚呢位人兄, 同時作出呼籲, 雖然秒經, 但都要一再呼籲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對住廢老一定要零容忍<br />\n有咩事一定要惡, 仲要惡撚過佢地, 屌到佢地仆街<br />\n千祈唔好怯, 怯就柒一世</span>"},{"pid":"617171d6bf8c6f10f1740625144dba811e94c08e","tid":991474,"uid":157362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T11:45:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e26e47e62f9f4a0fbe464c385e47cbcdd82c399","tid":991474,"uid":113335,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T12:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/61SgvdZDvYkMekDWAh/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F61SgvdZDvYkMekDWAh%2Fgiphy.gif&h=b0bac806&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e6273c6f6303d9132560b8f548119a1c6ef24c6","tid":991474,"uid":64155,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T12:20:02.000Z","msg":"Ho ball"},{"pid":"4c4ff10ce0134f7eff62afc7b481c6a5f30208df","tid":991474,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T12:22:50.000Z","msg":"事實"},{"pid":"10e8947011da290d11ffc11d389f9886739bc7a1","tid":991474,"uid":153239,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T12:23:28.000Z","msg":"落車果陣 一見到個廢老係門口standby<br />\n我每次都q埋雙手之後抬一抬高個頭 望撚住佢<br />\n<br />\nd廢老都會縮埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後係點都要行中間出去<br />\n佢唔郁就撞9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5e99f6727a72b20a95387210458bd0292c547d","tid":991474,"uid":125073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T12:24:23.000Z","msg":"點解唔除褲嘅"},{"pid":"0ddc202e3d97bd1e68c45a90142d00ca0cd81b07","tid":991474,"uid":37431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T12:27:41.000Z",